PrecisAuthority for (a) the Minister of Foreign Affairs OR Keith Christie, Ambassador of Canada to Cuba, to sign an Exchange of Notes with the Republic of Cuba extending an agreement on HIGHJACKING OF AIRCRAFT AND VESSELS AND OTHER OFFENCES (1973); and (b) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the necessary action to bring the Agreement into force for Canada.
